"dashboards <dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards>` som en användare "
"har :ref:`beviljats åtkomst <dashboards/access-and-sharing>` till, "
"grupperade efter sektion."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:58
