"anger du "
"sedan :guilabel:`Username`, :guilabel:`Password`, :guilabel:`Domain` "
"och :guilabel:`Display Name`. När du är klar trycker du på :guilabel:`Login`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/devices_integrations.rst:182
msgid ""
"At this point, Linphone is ready to start making calls, once there is a "
