"chart` :guilabel:`diagram`-ikonen, t.ex. :icon:`fa-bar-chart` *(#1) "
"Försäljningsanalys*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/visualize_data/charts.rst:59
msgid ""
