#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:159
msgid "Select the business portfolio"
msgstr "Välj företagsportfölj"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:161
msgid ""
"The last step of the app creation process is to connect a business portfolio."
msgstr ""
"Det sista steget i processen för att skapa appen är att ansluta en "
"företagsportfölj."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:163
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Business portfolio - Optional`, click the drop-down menu "
"and select the Meta business account profile. Review the *Meta Platform "
"Terms* and *Developer Policies* agreements, then click :guilabel:`Create "
"app` to accept and create the app."
msgstr ""
"Under :guilabel:`Business portfolio - Optional`, klicka på rullgardinsmenyn "
"och välj Meta-företagskontouppgiften. Granska *Meta Platform Terms* och "
"*Developer Policies*-avtalen, klicka sedan på :guilabel:`Skapa app` för att "
"acceptera och skapa appen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:167
msgid ""
"To accept the agreements and create the app, enter the Facebook account "
"password and click :guilabel:`Submit`. The browser then redirects to "
"the :guilabel:`Meta for Developers` dashboard."
msgstr ""
"För att acceptera avtalen och skapa appen, ange Facebook-kontots lösenord "
"och klicka på :guilabel:`Skicka in`. Webbläsaren omdirigerar sedan "
"till :guilabel:`Meta for Developers` Dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:171
msgid ""
"If the Meta business account is prohibited from advertising, the app cannot "
"be claimed. To resolve this issue, navigate to `Meta Business Suite <https://"
"business.facebook.com/business>`__ for assistance."
msgstr ""
"Om Meta-företagskontot är förbjudet från annonsering kan appen inte tas i "
"anspråk. För att lösa detta problem, navigera till `Meta Business Suite "
"<https://business.facebook.com/business>`__ för hjälp."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:175
msgid ""
"For more information, see `Meta's documentation on advertising restrictions "
"<https://www.facebook.com/business/help/975570072950669>`_."
msgstr ""
"För mer information, se `Meta's dokumentation om reklamrestriktioner "
"<https://www.facebook.com/business/help/975570072950669>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:181
msgid "Add a WhatsApp product to the app"
msgstr "Lägg till en WhatsApp-produkt i appen"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:183
msgid ""
"Now that the basic structure of the app has been created, a product needs to "
"be added to the app. Navigate to the `Meta Developer Dashboard <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/apps>`__, and click on the app that is being "
"configured. The page redirects to the app's dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Nu när appens grundläggande struktur har skapats måste en produkt läggas "
"till i appen. Gå till `Meta Developer Dashboard <https://"
"developers.facebook.com/apps>`__ och klicka på den app som konfigureras. "
"Sidan omdirigerar till appens dashboard."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:187
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Add products to your app`, go to WhatsApp near the bottom "
"of the page and click :guilabel:`Set up`."
msgstr ""
"Under :guilabel:`Add products to your app`, gå till WhatsApp nära sidans "
"nederkant och klicka på :guilabel:`Installera`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:191
msgid ""
"`Meta's WhatsApp developer documentation <https://developers.facebook.com/"
"docs/whatsapp/>`__"
msgstr ""
"`Metas WhatsApp-utvecklardokumentation <https://developers.facebook.com/docs/"
"whatsapp/>`__"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:193
msgid ""
"The browser then redirects to the configuration page for "
"the :guilabel:`WhatsApp Business Platform API`."
msgstr ""
"Webbläsaren omdirigerar sedan till konfigurationssidan "
"för :guilabel:`WhatsApp Business Platform API`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:196
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Select a Meta Business Account` option, select the Meta "
"business to be configured, then click :guilabel:`Continue` to confirm the "
"selection and agree to Meta's terms and conditions as linked on "
"the :guilabel:`Meta App Dashboard`."
msgstr ""
"Under :guilabel:`Select a Meta Business Account`-alternativet, välj det Meta-"
"företag som ska konfigureras, klicka sedan på :guilabel:`Fortsätt` för att "
"bekräfta valet och godkänna Metas villkor enligt länkarna på :guilabel:`Meta "
"App Dashboard`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:200
msgid ""
"Once the WhatsApp product is added to the app, Meta provides a WhatsApp test "
"phone number. This test phone number can send unlimited messages to a "
"maximum of five recipients."
msgstr ""
"När WhatsApp-produkten har lagts till i appen tillhandahåller Meta ett "
"WhatsApp-testnummer. Detta testnummer kan skicka obegränsat antal "
"meddelanden till maximalt fem mottagare."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:203
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Send and receive messages`, select the :guilabel:`To` field "
"and choose :guilabel:`Manage phone number list`. Add up to five valid "
"WhatsApp number as recipients, then enter the confirmation codes sent to "
"those phone numbers in WhatsApp to verify."
msgstr ""
"Under :guilabel:`Send and receive messages`, välj :guilabel:`Till`-fältet "
"och välj :guilabel:`Hantera telefonnummerlista`. Lägg till upp till fem "
"giltiga WhatsApp-nummer som mottagare, ange sedan bekräftelsekoderna som "
"skickats till dessa telefonnummer i WhatsApp för att verifiera."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:208
msgid ""
"`WhatsApp Cloud API guide <https://developers.facebook.com/docs/whatsapp/"
"cloud-api/get-started#add-recipient-number>`__"
msgstr ""
"`WhatsApp Cloud API-guide <https://developers.facebook.com/docs/whatsapp/"
"cloud-api/get-started#add-recipient-number>`__"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:214
msgid "WhatsApp API quickstart"
msgstr "WhatsApp API snabbstart"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:216
msgid ""
"Once the Meta accounts and app have been configured, "
"click :guilabel:`Continue` to proceed to the WhatsApp :guilabel:`Quickstart` "
"page. This page provides a starting point for configuring the WhatsApp API "
"by adding a phone number and sending an initial test message."
msgstr ""
"När Meta-kontona och appen har konfigurerats, klicka på :guilabel:`Fortsätt` "
"för att gå vidare till WhatsApp :guilabel:`Snabbstart`-sidan. Denna sida ger "
"en utgångspunkt för att konfigurera WhatsApp API genom att lägga till ett "
"telefonnummer och skicka ett första testmeddelande."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:221
msgid ""
"If the browser does not automatically redirect to the "
"WhatsApp :guilabel:`Quickstart` page, navigate to the `Meta Developer "
"Dashboard <https://developers.facebook.com/apps>`__ and select the `Odoo` "
"app."
msgstr ""
"Om webbläsaren inte automatiskt omdirigerar till "
"WhatsApp :guilabel:`Quickstart`-sidan, navigera till `Meta Developer "
"Dashboard <https://developers.facebook.com/apps>`__ och välj appen `Odoo`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:225
msgid ""
"In the menu on the left-hand side of the page, click the :icon:`fa-chevron-"
"down` :guilabel:`(down chevron)` icon next to the :guilabel:`WhatsApp` "
"section heading. A small menu opens, containing the following options:"
msgstr ""
"I menyn på vänster sida av sidan, klicka på :icon:`fa-chevron-"
"down` :guilabel:`(nedåtpil)`-ikonen bredvid :guilabel:`WhatsApp`-"
"sektionsrubriken. En liten meny öppnas som innehåller följande optioner:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:229
msgid ":guilabel:`Quickstart`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Snabb start`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:230
msgid ":guilabel:`API setup`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Installation av programmeringsgränssnitt`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:231
msgid ":guilabel:`Configuration`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Konfiguration`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:233
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Quickstart` option, and then click :guilabel:`Start "
"using the API`."
msgstr ""
"Klicka på alternativet :guilabel:`Snabbstart` och sedan på :guilabel:`Börja "
"använda API`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:238
msgid "API setup"
msgstr "Installation av programmeringsgränssnitt"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:240
msgid ""
"After clicking on :guilabel:`Start using the API`, the page navigates to "
"the :guilabel:`API setup`. Now that the test number has been created, a test "
"message can be sent to confirm that WhatsApp is working properly. Navigate "
"to the :guilabel:`Send and receive messages` section. Under :guilabel:`Step "
"1 Select phone numbers`, click the drop-down menu next to :guilabel:`To`."
msgstr ""
"Efter att ha klickat på :guilabel:`Start using the API`, navigerar sidan "
"till :guilabel:`Installation av programmeringsgränssnitt`. Nu när testnumret "
"har skapats kan ett testmeddelande skickas för att bekräfta att WhatsApp "
"fungerar korrekt. Navigera till sektionen :guilabel:`Send and receive "
"messages`. Under :guilabel:`Step 1 Select phone numbers`, klicka på "
"rullgardinsmenyn bredvid :guilabel:`To`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:245
msgid ""
"Next, select the only option available: :guilabel:`Manage phone number "
"list`. Follow the steps and add up to five phone numbers to send the free "
"test messages to. Enter the appropriate country code and phone number, then "
"click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"Välj sedan det enda tillgängliga alternativet: :guilabel:`Hantera "
"telefonnummerlista`. Följ stegen och lägg till upp till fem telefonnummer "
"att skicka de kostnadsfria testmeddelandena till. Ange lämplig landskod och "
"telefonnummer, klicka sedan på :guilabel:`Nästa`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:250
msgid ""
"Adding a phone number to send to in this step allows for a successful test "
"to be sent by the terminal. This is critical to ensure the "
"WhatsApp :abbr:`API (Application Programming Interface)` is working."
msgstr ""
"Att lägga till ett telefonnummer att skicka till i detta steg möjliggör att "
"ett lyckat test kan skickas via terminalen. Detta är kritiskt för att "
"säkerställa att WhatsApp :abbr:`Programmeringsgränssnitt (Application "
"Programming Interface)` fungerar."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:254
msgid ""
"On the next page, enter the verification code sent to the phone numbers, and "
"click :guilabel:`Next` to verify the numbers."
msgstr ""
"På nästa sida, ange verifieringskoden som skickats till telefonnumren och "
"klicka på :guilabel:`Nästa` för att verifiera numren."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:260
msgid "Send a test message via terminal"
msgstr "Skicka ett testmeddelande via terminal"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:262
msgid ""
"Once the phone number has been verified, send a test message via the "
"terminal. Under :guilabel:`Step 2 Send messages with the API`, "
"click :guilabel:`Send Message`. This should send a test message to the phone "
"numbers that were added."
msgstr ""
"När telefonnumret har verifierats, skicka ett testmeddelande via terminalen. "
"Under :guilabel:`Step 2 Send messages with the API`, klicka "
"på :guilabel:`Skicka meddelande`. Detta bör skicka ett testmeddelande till "
"telefonnumren som lades till."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:266
msgid ""
"Upon successfully receiving the message to the numbers, move onto the next "
"section to :ref:`produce and configure webhooks <productivity/whatsapp/"
"webhooks>`."
msgstr ""
"När meddelandet har tagits emot på numren, gå vidare till nästa avsnitt för "
"att :ref:`skapa och konfigurera webhooks <productivity/whatsapp/webhooks>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:272
msgid "WhatsApp configuration in Odoo"
msgstr "WhatsApp-konfiguration i Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:274
msgid ""
"To create a :guilabel:`Callback URL` and :guilabel:`Webhook Verify Token`, "
"the phone number, token, app ID, and account ID need to be configured in "
"Odoo; these values are used to set up webhooks, which make it possible to "
"receive messages in the database. The configuration steps in this section "
"are all performed in the Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"För att skapa en :guilabel:`Callback URL` och :guilabel:`Webhook Verify "
"Token`, behöver telefonnummer, token, app-ID och konto-ID konfigureras i "
"Odoo; dessa värden används för att ställa in webhooks, vilket gör det "
"möjligt att ta emot meddelanden i databasen. Konfigurationsstegen i detta "
"avsnitt utförs alla i Odoo-databasen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:279
msgid ""
"In Odoo, navigate to :menuselection:`WhatsApp app --> Configuration --> "
"WhatsApp Business Accounts`, then click :guilabel:`New` to configure the "
"WhatsApp business account in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"I Odoo, navigera till :menuselection:`WhatsApp-app --> Konfiguration --> "
"WhatsApp-företagskonton`, klicka sedan på :guilabel:`Ny` för att konfigurera "
"WhatsApp-företagskontot i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/whatsapp.rst:282
msgid ""
"In another browser tab, navigate to `Meta Developer Dashboard <https://"
"developers.facebook.com>`__. Select :menuselection:`My Apps --> WhatsApp --> "
"API Configuration`, and then copy the following values from the Meta "
"developer console into the corresponding fields in Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"I en annan webbläsarflik, navigera till `Meta Developer Dashboard <https://"
"developers.facebook.com>`__. Välj :menuselection:`My Apps --> WhatsApp --> "
"API Configuration`, och kopiera sedan följande värden från Metas "
"utvecklarkonsol till motsvarande fält i Odoo:"

